# Client / build-time env (Vite import.meta.env). PUBLIC — safe to commit a real
# value, but kept out of git by convention. Copy to `.env` and fill in.
#
# Clerk publishable key (pk_test_... in dev, pk_live_... in prod).
# In CI, set this as a GitHub Actions *variable* so the production build can
# bake it into the client bundle.
VITE_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
